# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# QUICK SARI EMAIL CONFIGURATION (.env)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Your real Gmail address (e.g. your.name@gmail.com)
EMAIL_USER=your_email@gmail.com

# Your Gmail App Password (NOT your regular password!)
# 1. Go to your Google Account -> Security
# 2. Enable 2-Step Verification if you haven't already.
# 3. Search for "App Passwords"
# 4. Generate a new password for "Mail" / "Other"
# 5. Paste the 16-character code below (no spaces):
EMAIL_PASS=xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx
